manifest_analysis.title:
Clear text traffic is Enabled For App
[android:usesCleartextTraffic=true]
manifest_analysis.desc: The app intends to use cleartext network traffic, such as cleartext HTTP, FTP stacks, DownloadManager, and MediaPlayer. The default value for apps that target API level 27 or lower is "true". Apps that target API level 28 or higher default to "false". The key reason for avoiding cleartext traffic is the lack of confidentiality, authenticity, and protections against tampering; a network attacker can eavesdrop on transmitted data and also modify it without being detected.
manifest_analysis.name: Clear text traffic is Enabled For App [android:usesCleartextTraffic=true]

manifest_analysis.title:
Application Data can be Backed up
[android:allowBackup] flag is missing.
manifest_analysis.desc: The flag [android:allowBackup] should be set to false. By default it is set to true and allows anyone to backup your application data via adb. It allows users who have enabled USB debugging to copy application data off of the device.
manifest_analysis.name: Application Data can be Backed up [android:allowBackup] flag is missing.

manifest_analysis.title:
Broadcast Receiver (com.google.firebase.iid.FirebaseInstanceIdReceiver) is Protected by a permission, but the protection level of the permission should be checked.
Permission: com.google.android.c2dm.permission.SEND
[android:exported=true]
manifest_analysis.desc: A Broadcast Receiver is found to be shared with other apps on the device therefore leaving it accessible to any other application on the device. It is protected by a permission which is not defined in the analysed application. As a result, the protection level of the permission should be checked where it is defined. If it is set to normal or dangerous, a malicious application can request and obtain the permission and interact with the component. If it is set to signature, only applications signed with the same certificate can obtain the permission.
manifest_analysis.name: is Protected by a permission, but the protection level of the permission should be checked.[android:exported=true]

metadata.description: Query Database of SMS, Contacts etc
The App logs information. Sensitive information should never be logged.

The App uses an insecure Random Number Generator.
metadata.cwe: CWE-330 Use of Insufficiently Random Values

playstore_details.title: B4U Wallet: Crypto Bitcoin Wallet Exchange
playstore_details.description:
B4U Wallet Exchange allows you to secure, manage, and exchange your favourite crypto & fiat currencies like Bitcoin, Rscoin, Euro, USD and more from a beautiful, easy to use mobile wallet that puts you in control of your wealth.

Manage your wealth in a blockchain wallet that combines solid engineering and beautiful design in the form of live charts, news, announcements that update in real-time.

Buy and sell one digital asset for another without having to go through centralised exchanges. Exchange cryptocurrencies in just a few taps from the comfort of your wallet while maintaining privacy and control.

All of this and more give you the way to join the new financial system that you’ve been waiting for.

SECURE YOUR WEALTH
Don’t give control to centralized wallets and exchanges that can suffer from hacks and lose your funds. B4U Wallet Exchange encrypts transaction data on your device so that no one can access your cryptocurrency but you. You can also Enable Face or Touch ID to conveniently secure your wallet without having to type your passcode.

TRACK YOUR PORTFOLIO/HISTORY
Track your cryptocurrency portfolio and its performance over time with B4U Wallets’ stunning and intuitive charts that update in real-time so that you can keep up with the fast-moving market.

BUY AND SELL ONE CRYPTOCURRENCY FOR ANOTHER
Use the built-in exchange feature to quickly and easily buy and sell one cryptocurrency for another – all without having to sign up for an account.

SEND AND RECEIVE DIGITAL CURRENCY
Need to send or receive Bitcoin or other digital currencies? Send and receive any of the many supported blockchain assets with the touch of a button using text addresses or QR codes.

ALL OF YOUR FAVORITE ASSETS, IN ONE WALLET
Forget having to download a bunch of different wallets and write down a recovery phrase. Store your favorite assets like Bitcoin, Ethereum, Ripple, Rscoin, and more in a wallet that always continues to add its users’ favorite assets.

SUPPORTED CRYPTOCURRENCIES & FIAT CURRENCIES
(Buy, store, exchange and spend)

CRYPTOCURREINCES LIST:
Bitcoin (BTC)
Ethereum (ETH)
Ripple (XRP)
Bitcoin Cash (BCH)
Litecoin (LTC)
Rscoin (RSC)
Dash (DASH)
Zcash (ZEC)
Bitcoin cash (BCH)

FIAT CURRENCIES LIST:
Malaysian Ringgit (MYR)
Singapore Dollar (SGD)
Us Dollar (USD)
Euro (EUR)

24/7 WORLD-CLASS SUPPORT
Get your questions answered fast by using our extensive online help desk or by contacting our 24/7 global human support team.

WORLD-CLASS DESIGN AND ENGINEERING
B4U Wallet brings you an experience that combines the best of design and engineering. Our team has experience designing experiences for the likes of Apple, BMW, Disney, Louis Vuitton, Microsoft, and Nike. Engineering-wise, we’ve published over 200 open-source libraries and written code in use by most Bitcoin and cryptocurrency software out there.

ABOUT B4U WALLET EXCHANGE
B4U Wallet Exchange gives users a way to depart the legacy system and join the blockchain revolution without taking away what made it revolutionary in the first place: elimination of middlemen like banks, brokers, and exchanges, as well as privacy and control of one’s wealth not just for oneself but for future generations.

B4U Wallet Exchange is a cryptocurrency wallet and exchange platform. Provides a multi-chain cryptocurrency wallet to store Bitcoin, Ethereum, Dashcoin, Litecoin, Ripple, etc. Offers a web-based and smartphone wallet for Android and iOS.

Want to learn more?
Visit us at https://b4uwallet.com/
